"{\"uid\": \"intermatwrestle.com-articles.html-international-hildebrandt-downs-world-medalist-feng-to-move-into-olympic-semifinals-r99429\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Forgot your password?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 21, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Earl Smith  Earl Smith\\u2022August 6, 2024  Day two of wrestling at the 2024 Olympic Games started off with a bang - and it had nothing to do with any American wrestlers.\", \"from\": 23, \"to\": 188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23, \"end\": 33, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earl_Smith_(catcher)\", \"score\": 0.6036270195754082, \"rank\": 0.4887218045113575, \"text\": \"Earl Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earl_Smith_(catcher)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earl_Smith_(catcher)\"}, {\"begin\": 35, \"end\": 45, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earl_Smith_(catcher)\", \"score\": 0.6036270195754082, \"rank\": 0.4887218045113575, \"text\": \"Earl Smith\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earl_Smith_(catcher)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Earl_Smith_(catcher)\"}, {\"begin\": 169, \"end\": 187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Wrestlers\", \"score\": 0.9999891861560067, \"rank\": 1.0809094597902368e-05, \"text\": \"American wrestlers\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Wrestlers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Wrestlers\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the very first match of the 50 kg weight class, 2020 Olympic champion Yui Susaki (Japan) who is also a three-time world champion, riding an 82-match winning streak was stunned by India's Vinesh Phogat, 3-2.\", \"from\": 189, \"to\": 398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 262, \"end\": 272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yui_Susaki\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yui Susaki\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yui_Susaki\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yui_Susaki\"}, {\"begin\": 274, \"end\": 279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5855386513019555, \"rank\": 0.5884945931546182, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 371, \"end\": 376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"score\": 0.999918960553402, \"rank\": 8.056986641656646e-05, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q12973014\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India_national_cricket_team\"}, {\"begin\": 379, \"end\": 392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh Phogat\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Phogat hung close to Susaki for the entire match and attacked late in the final period to shock Susaki and the entire wrestling world.\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 533, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 420, \"end\": 426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Susaki,_K\\u014dchi\", \"score\": 0.9780506064408127, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Susaki\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Susaki,_K\\u014dchi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Susaki,_K\\u014dchi\"}, {\"begin\": 495, \"end\": 501, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Susaki,_K\\u014dchi\", \"score\": 0.9780506064408127, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Susaki\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Susaki,_K\\u014dchi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Susaki,_K\\u014dchi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It marked the first loss by Susaki to a non-Japanese opponent.\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 562, \"end\": 568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Susaki,_K\\u014dchi\", \"score\": 0.9780506064408127, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Susaki\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Susaki,_K\\u014dchi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Susaki,_K\\u014dchi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Staying in the 50 kg weight class, American Sarah Hildebrandt got her tournament started with a dominant 10-0 tech fall over Algeria's Ibtissem Doudou.\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 633, \"end\": 641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999103833260362, \"rank\": 8.826410703378969e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 642, \"end\": 659, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Hildebrandt\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sarah Hildebrandt\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Hildebrandt\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Hildebrandt\"}, {\"begin\": 723, \"end\": 730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9804229904129587, \"rank\": 0.019967907997826554, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Early in the opening period, Hildebrandt got to Doudou's legs and earned a takedown.\", \"from\": 750, \"to\": 834, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She quickly ended the contest with four of her trademark leg laces.\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 902, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That win set up a quarterfinal clash with fellow 2023 World bronze medalist Ziqi Feng (China).\", \"from\": 904, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 980, \"end\": 984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ziqi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ziqi\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ziqi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ziqi\"}, {\"begin\": 991, \"end\": 996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9989164947327692, \"rank\": 0.0007934151182679399, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Feng got on the scoreboard first with a double-leg for a takedown.\", \"from\": 999, \"to\": 1065, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hildebrandt never gave up and bellied out, rather choosing to wrestle through the position.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After deftly avoiding exposure points, Hildebrandt was able to gain a reversal and trailed 2-1.\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Shortly after a restart, the two found themselves in a position that would come up time and again in this contest.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1369, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hildebrandt with a front headlock.\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1404, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In this instance, the American unleashed a beautiful shuck which resulted in a takedown and a 3-2 lead.\", \"from\": 1405, \"to\": 1508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1427, \"end\": 1435, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999103833260362, \"rank\": 8.826410703378969e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Later in the period, that position came up again and Hildebrandt tried another shuck.\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1594, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This time, Feng was ready and held strong before getting to Hildebrandt's legs for a takedown.\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1689, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Near the end of the opening period, Hildebrandt unleashed a picture-esque ankle pick.\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That shot did not directly lead to a takedown; however, Hildebrandt was able to spin behind her stunned opponent for a takedown and a 5-4 lead heading into the break.\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1942, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For most of the final period, Hildebrandt was able to prevent Feng from getting to an advantageous position.\", \"from\": 1944, \"to\": 2052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The biggest flurry of the period came with about :45 seconds left in the contest, as the pair ended up in that familiar front headlock position again.\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of going back to the shuck, Hildebrandt showed her variety of short offense and blocked off an arm and spun for an insurance takedown.\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2346, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That 7-4 lead held up and Hildebrandt advanced to this afternoon's semifinals.\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the semis, Hildebrandt will meet a familiar foe - Mongolia's Otgonjargal Dolgorjav.\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2514, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The two met in the world semifinals in each of the last two years.\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2581, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2022 Dolgorjav was victorious 6-2.\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2619, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year, she won 7-5.\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2643, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sandwiched in between those two matches was a 10-0 win for Hildebrandt at the 2023 Hungarian Ranking Series event.\", \"from\": 2644, \"to\": 2758, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Turning our attention to the men's Greco-Roman portion of the tournament, the first American to take the mat on Tuesday was Kamal Bey at 77 kg.\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2795, \"end\": 2806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greco-Roman_wrestling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.004822719841627e-44, \"text\": \"Greco-Roman\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greco-Roman_wrestling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greco-Roman_wrestling\"}, {\"begin\": 2844, \"end\": 2852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999103833260362, \"rank\": 8.826410703378969e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 2884, \"end\": 2889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamal_Haasan\", \"score\": 0.9835786524122664, \"rank\": 0.016695510365848848, \"text\": \"Kamal\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamal_Haasan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamal_Haasan\"}, {\"begin\": 2890, \"end\": 2893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.999999999521151, \"rank\": 4.0925121857103837e-10, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bey also had an opponent he's met multiple times over the years - Akzhol Makhmudov.\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 2987, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2904, \"end\": 2907, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.999999999521151, \"rank\": 4.0925121857103837e-10, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two-time world champion and 2020 Olympic silver medalist from Kyrgyzstan lost to Bey in the 2017 Junior World finals.\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 3109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3054, \"end\": 3064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyrgyzstan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9994161948537832, \"rank\": 0.00058414617383248, \"text\": \"Kyrgyzstan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyrgyzstan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kyrgyzstan_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3073, \"end\": 3076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.999999999521151, \"rank\": 4.0925121857103837e-10, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In this meeting, there was little action in the first period which led to a passivity call on Bey.\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3209, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3205, \"end\": 3208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.999999999521151, \"rank\": 4.0925121857103837e-10, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Makhmudov was given plenty of time to work from the par terre position, but could not add to his lead and the match went into period two, 1-0.\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the second, Makhmudov turned up the heat on Bey and would not allow him near the center of the mat, garnering back-to-back push-out points and a 3-0 lead.\", \"from\": 3354, \"to\": 3511, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3401, \"end\": 3404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.999999999521151, \"rank\": 4.0925121857103837e-10, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A second passivity call on Bey made the match 4-0.\", \"from\": 3512, \"to\": 3562, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3539, \"end\": 3542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.999999999521151, \"rank\": 4.0925121857103837e-10, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once again, Makhmudov could not turn Bey from the par terre restart.\", \"from\": 3563, \"to\": 3631, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3600, \"end\": 3603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.999999999521151, \"rank\": 4.0925121857103837e-10, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Late in the contest, Bey was able to get on the board with a push-out of his own; however, it was not enough and he fell 4-1.\", \"from\": 3632, \"to\": 3757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3653, \"end\": 3656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.999999999521151, \"rank\": 4.0925121857103837e-10, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In his next bout, Makhmudov was shocked by Demeu Zhadrayev (Kazakhstan) late in the second period.\", \"from\": 3759, \"to\": 3857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3819, \"end\": 3829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakhstan\", \"score\": 0.9999999794940779, \"rank\": 2.0504226116831174e-08, \"text\": \"Kazakhstan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakhstan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kazakhstan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhadrayev was able to expose Makhmudov from a front head-pinch maneuver which gave him a 3-1 win.\", \"from\": 3858, \"to\": 3955, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The loss from Makhmudov eliminated Bey from medal contention.\", \"from\": 3956, \"to\": 4017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3991, \"end\": 3994, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.999999999521151, \"rank\": 4.0925121857103837e-10, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also in action was Joe Rau at 97 kg.\", \"from\": 4019, \"to\": 4055, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4038, \"end\": 4041, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"score\": 0.9891431196856799, \"rank\": 0.010831920436216206, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\"}, {\"begin\": 4042, \"end\": 4045, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Okka_Rau\", \"score\": 0.8963129913825975, \"rank\": 0.11568169004230344, \"text\": \"Rau\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Okka_Rau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Okka_Rau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like Bey, Rau drew a past world champion in Iran's Mohammadhadi Saravi.\", \"from\": 4056, \"to\": 4127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4061, \"end\": 4064, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.999999999521151, \"rank\": 4.0925121857103837e-10, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}, {\"begin\": 4066, \"end\": 4069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Okka_Rau\", \"score\": 0.8963129913825975, \"rank\": 0.11568169004230344, \"text\": \"Rau\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://db